{"tid":1519944,"cid":12,"subCid":0,"title":"（父母和解文）實測過4個冷戰中既家庭 100%可行","createTime":"2019-08-30T16:24:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-30T18:21:58.000Z","uid":263103,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"8e6c679b22b637e7f5aa3a0f19e4f9ff4c29fb8e","tid":1519944,"uid":263103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T16:24:57.000Z","msg":"建議你地用以下最安靜既方式感染佢地 <br />\n<br />\n準備一堆長輩圖 同埋因果既文宣<br />\n<br />\n 上面寫一張紙條，內容如下:<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;希望你地可以安靜睇晒啲資料<br />\n<br />\n如果我有收人錢 就唔駛仲留屋企 發左達唔駛再出去<br />\n如果大家有收錢 警方咁要面 做完卧底後一定公告天下 <br />\n但到而家都無提 係證明左你地當初信既野一開始就係假 係要來呃你地去阻我地抗爭 <br />\n而最後得益唔係你地 都唔係我地 而係奸商貪腐官員同黑社會<br />\n<br />\n我無野想再講&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />幾家人都冷靜左 和好如初左返 <br />\n想佢地明白自己 首先要自己唔好忽略 指控同放棄家人<br />\n<br />\n一家人都要做到不割席 不分化 不篤灰 齊上齊落 <br />\n親手令場抗爭幫我地得到更多 而不是失去更多<br />\n<br />\n希望小小分享可以幫到大家 雖然我p牌 但發誓無吹水"},{"pid":"6b54834c8560a24468a270617f136f99b7190953","tid":1519944,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T16:26:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Qw3QgZA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQw3QgZA.jpg&h=c3ca146d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n九月一號下午一點機場見<br />\n<br />\n901機場和你塞 Channel<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=7hybd32tUfzicQL4e%2Fav0iHfnck7qU2fF1mVfqY7ZMk%3D&h=a554a842\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 公海<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyouopen&d=7hybd32tUfzicQL4e%2Fav0iHfnck7qU2fF1mVfqY7ZMk%3D&h=cc54fdee\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 宣傳<br />\n<